Ilename: fy_rampage_v2
filesize:1.27MB
DATE RELEASED: Dec. 11th 2006

CREDITS: would like to credit my clan..BD (BULLET DODGERS) and all public users for testing
for me

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS:

1.extract .bsp and .nav files into your mycomp/local/programfiles/valve/steam/steamapps/user/counterstrikesource/cstrike/maps folder

2. open/restart counter strike source, go to create server and play alone,LAN or with bots.


DESCRIPTION:A cool map with unique lighting, bunch of secret places with illusion walls and doors, real dark in some places, brighter in other areas.
WARNING:BLINKING LIGHTS DONT PLAY WITH SEIZURE PROBLEMS
